productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Julisa has one of these. She works as a bartender and she says it looks crooked.
one of my hobbies is antique-shopping. and when i'm antique-shopping this works great.
The box this comes in is 5 light-year by 6 foot and weights 17 megaton!!!
heard about this on gypsy jazz radio, decided to give it a try.
